  "comment": "BT400 Lightweight Par 12x 10W RGBW: The BT-4 series is a range of high powered LED pars built into a slimline ABS housing so it can fit in the tightest of spaces like box truss. These fixtures are equipped with a power-connector in/out for daisy chaining multiple units together. All BT4 models have pre-set programs that can be used in stand-alone mode. In the DMX settings there is the choice of different DMX modes with pre-set colour macro's or a mode where you can control every single colour individually per section. The same can be done in stand-alone mode with the supplied remote control. The robust ABS housing and double stand also make the BT Pars ideal for rental as they are lightweight and easy to setup. Ideal for DJs, bands, stages and venues wanting a great colour wash.",
